{"tid":1972223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銅鑼灣書店4.25台北重開 林榮基寄語港人: 「仍可以做好多嘢」「 繼續抗爭」","createTime":"2020-04-14T11:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T12:32:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2532424cd332710f8a5ee6ee48626a1604ab2a18","tid":1972223,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】香港銅鑼灣書店將在台灣重生。因港府修訂逃犯條例而被迫流亡台灣的銅鑼灣書店前店主林榮基，本月25日踏足台灣剛好一年。林榮基昨表示，銅鑼灣書店本月25日將在台北重開。他希望香港人繼續抗爭，不要放棄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/_8GooPdP6LW4ZoUlx7N_fQbvS-U=/802x552/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/EQFK6B5M22OGLT34L3INH7MHRI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F_8GooPdP6LW4ZoUlx7N_fQbvS-U%3D%2F802x552%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FEQFK6B5M22OGLT34L3INH7MHRI.gif&h=25da7e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林榮基寄語港人面對強權打壓不要放棄。 張貴翔攝<br />\n<br />\n林榮基寄語港人繼續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命」是香港抗爭者耳熟能詳的口號，將於本月25日在台北重開的銅鑼灣書店，店內掛上「光復香港，時代革命」黑底黃字的橫額。林榮基去年12月起着手重開書店，選址一度考慮年輕人熱點、台北西門町等地，最後敲定和香港銅鑼灣有幾分相似的台北捷運中山站一帶。經過近三個月籌備，書店近日已取得商業登記，上書工作也大致完成，林榮基因此敲定本月25日重開。<br />\n<br />\n「既然一間小書店也有辦法重開，我們仍然可以繼續抗爭，尚未去到絕境，在外面仍可以做好多嘢。銅鑼灣書店在台灣重開也是一個證明，只要理念不變，人在外也可以保持你的理念。」林榮基表示，香港過去一年的變化堪稱翻天覆地，完全是兩個世界，中共對香港的箝制較一年前有過之而無不及。不過，他認為香港人不是沒路可走，仍有退一步的可能。他希望香港人繼續抗爭，不要放棄，但前提是先保護自己，特別是年輕人，「香港待不下去，也有後路走，不要灰心」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200411/large/1586533332_87a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200411%2Flarge%2F1586533332_87a7.gif&h=bb6dbbe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200411/WWBFL4NCXCRYNZUEJD5UAKRNBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200411%2FWWBFL4NCXCRYNZUEJD5UAKRNBU%2F&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=f398c81c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200411%2FWWBFL4NCXCRYNZUEJD5UAKRNBU%2F&h=f5f3e5d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200411/WWBFL4NCXCRYNZUEJD5UAKRNBU/</a>"},{"pid":"711181cb48d5e24b69e68d7544e44dcbddaf188b","tid":1972223,"uid":155818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:39:37.000Z","msg":"仲記得佢之前想水流亡台灣班手足返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc90bed5a84b6075cd77c22a73e87a72360b039","tid":1972223,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"你今日好勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a0e2b79d0fb54a701fe38afc056a6a731706b5","tid":1972223,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cc90bed5a84b6075cd77c22a73e87a72360b039","tid":1972223,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"你今日好勤力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"今日唔勤力都唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac4ceec108995a828d2b9d7c74b7aebcde4e047","tid":1972223,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:41:16.000Z","msg":"入嚟支持文宣手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swallowlife.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u